snippet.title: Slowly Sliding Ducks - Announcement Trailer 2025
snippet.description:
Wishlist it now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2485410/Slowly_Sliding_Ducks/

Stay afloat and navigate challenging waterpark rides against up to 16 online players. Spray water, slide, score, and aim to become the pool's most distinguished duck!
